title: 10 years ago, a Cowboys DE draftee named DeMarcus starred in a Super Bowl for another team. Could DeMarcus Lawrence become the second?

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: 10 years ago, a Cowboys DE draftee named DeMarcus starred in a Super Bowl for another team. Could DeMarcus Lawrence become the second?
sources.description: Another former longtime Cowboys player with the same first name, DeMarcus Ware, quickly won a Super Bowl after he left Dallas. Lawrence is hoping for the same outcome.
